{"tid":142767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鄭錦滿好彩] 醉駕殺人被告親屬法庭上嬉笑   遭法官當庭判入獄93日","createTime":"2017-03-04T05:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T08:59:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b33a864e44a322003d15faa2b1edff01d0914b","tid":142767,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"有片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bdi_iuRx-0o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBdi_iuRx-0o&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=6c92d2cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bdi_iuRx-0o</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.clickondetroit.com/photo/2017/02/24/Judge%20throws%20courtroom%20spectator%20in%20jail20170224111928_9040811_ver1.0_640_360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.clickondetroit.com%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2FJudge%2520throws%2520courtroom%2520spectator%2520in%2520jail20170224111928_9040811_ver1.0_640_360.jpg&h=827921e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國密西根州25歲的女子亞曼達（Amanda Kosal）去年酒駕撞死1名31歲的男子澤克（Jerome Zirker），留下同車重傷的未婚妻和5名孩子。亞曼達的親戚們卻在開庭旁聽時嘻笑，完全不當一回事，被審理的女法官里拉德（Qiana Lillard）訓斥警告並趕出法庭，沒想到亞曼達的母親唐娜（Donna Kosal）在走出門外後還不斷碎嘴叫囂，法官命令法警將她直接逮捕，當庭依藐視法庭罪判她坐93天的牢。<br />\n<br />\n亞曼達因酒駕肇事致人死亡，將面臨3到15年的有期徒刑。"},{"pid":"f642472c8aac33a05919c70c9f8f48b98d5ecab9","tid":142767,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"如果大家唔記得鄭錦滿搞邊科, 不妨回一回帶<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">法官陳慶偉指斥鄭錦滿：「唔好係法庭玩手機，你嚟呢度做咩？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56315884&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56315884%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170217&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=336b5cc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56315884%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170217&h=e3638151\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56315884&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170217</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s28.postimg.org/98micquel/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs28.postimg.org%2F98micquel%2Fimage.jpg&h=119e1868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n17名佔旺人士因於佔旺清場當日未有離開，前年遭律政司控告刑事藐視法庭，案件今在高院處理，其中被告「四眼哥哥」鄭錦滿及歐煜鈞認罪。鄭錦滿今遲了到庭，及後當資深大狀麥高義替他進行求情時，鄭坐在旁聽席上玩手機，結果被法官質疑其認罪誠意。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳慶偉指斥鄭錦滿：「唔好玩手機，你嚟呢度做咩？唔係你鍾意嚟就嚟，玩就玩，點睇倒你係有誠意道歉？」<br />\n<br />\n麥高義亦承認鄭的行為不尊重法庭，透露鄭差少許便可完成大學學位，亦承認案發時鄭背後有政治組織。鄭於庭外透露認罪是因為不想再跟對方糾纏，希望盡快完結這事。<br />\n<br />\n鄭於2014年11月佔旺清場當天，被警方拍得臉戴口罩、手持黃色橫額於示威區出現。"},{"pid":"2acd63e0fbc5f0aac1082a4ca9ae84cb8e9b3668","tid":142767,"uid":50359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"單野有後續，個阿嬸坐左一日之後再上庭喊晒口咁道歉 法官接收 當庭釋放"},{"pid":"f70d6e25494ddd91003bf6a7c46328d45858577a","tid":142767,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單野有後續，個阿嬸坐左一日之後再上庭喊晒口咁道歉 法官接收 當庭釋放</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 段片既後尾有"},{"pid":"2098cdce910f080f04339545abc70cc8e243813d","tid":142767,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>單野有後續，個阿嬸坐左一日之後再上庭喊晒口咁道歉 法官接收 當庭釋放</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係, 段片既後尾有</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1541b6e3757472a08d6ecfcacd43b90fdb6ba6cf","tid":142767,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77878633da1c6ff36f7335ccad234a26fbc52211","tid":142767,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:04:21.